Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're all out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then... wanna bet your pants\Nor something, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:02:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with Roshio, if you had won,\Nhe would have made you pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'll be taking all your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go. I won this money fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cheated just now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? When did I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did! You cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make ridiculous accusations, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarquiss! Sarquiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, too, didn't you?\NThis guy just cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That's right. He cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it, too. What a dirty cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me! You don't\Nknow who you're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Quit Dreaming!\NMock Town, the Town of Ridicule!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still don't see it, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't see it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Jaya island isn't that far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since the weather has\Nbeen stable for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should already be\Nin the island's climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Jaya must be a spring island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels nice and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the seagulls are enjoying it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhh! They were shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, let's make yakitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot? I didn't hear any gunfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I found a bullet! Considering\Nthe direction that they were flying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bullets came from the\Ndirection the ship's facing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that shots came from\Nan island that we can't even see yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was watching them the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what kind of eyesight, sniping skills\Nand rifle do you think this sniper has?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were shot somewhere else\Nand just happened to fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, we got seagulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing... He must've suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to kill one of them instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's also fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the result of how you lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Do you know who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I tell you, then?\NI'm the Fighting Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a neat-looking town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, doesn't it look kinda like a resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Resort?!\N--Hurry up, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it makes me feel like\NI want to stick around a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it my imagination, or do the ships\Nlined up in the harbor look like pirate ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly Usopp, since when can pirate ships\Njust openly line up in a harbor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! He's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister. You chose\Nthe wrong guy to beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that symbol. He's one of Roshio's gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of him, right?\NRoshio the Executioner,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose bounty is 42 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy, so you'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a reckless guy!\NThat wasn't a bogus game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing that he beat up\NRoshio the Executioner so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know? That's Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy?! Bellamy the Hyena,\Nthe one with a 55 million-Berry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bounty on his head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he needs a doctor! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, please hang on a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're all kinds of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a fun town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think those two can come\Nback without getting into trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the town looks dangerous as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's next to impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right. They can't do that!\N--H-Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Luffy! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she'll probably be okay,\Nsince those two are with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? If Nami-san's going, then I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, wh-what'll happen\Ni-i-if this ship is attacked...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, guess I'll prepare\Nsome tea and hold the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Where's Robin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...? She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun, about that tea...\N--Make it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this town, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...not fight. I give my word!\N--...not fight. I give my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. This is serious, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah...\N--Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the weak reply?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause trouble,\Nwe'll have to leave this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we won't be\Nable to go to the sky, got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, he fell from a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Looks like he's in pain.\N--Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you guys, sorry to bother you,\Nbut please help me get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to get up\Nby yourself, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy, get that side.\N--Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks... I'm on the horse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go, Stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horse, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't much of a reward,\Nbut would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too suspicious! We don't\Nwant any, so beat it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, apples! Thanks!\N--Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, some guys were eating apples\Nthat they got from a strange man,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then they exploded. Five of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Spit it out! Spit out\Nthe apple you just ate! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already swallowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's going too far!\N--It's a disaster inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ate a bad one,\Nyou would've died on the first bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is awful...\N--Hey, what the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roshio the Executioner's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks as if a war happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they fire a cannon or something\Nin the middle of the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Even people who\Nwere actually watching it said
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they couldn't tell what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is that Roshio's\Nopponent was Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bellamy the Hyena?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that he's got\Nthe power of one of the devil fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is up with this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't be so touchy, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got killed for no reason, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it happens sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be damned if it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many victims have there been now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he's a famous\Nwanted man. Who the heck is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't even wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we should stay away\Nfrom that Fighting Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to compete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... I wonder if we can really\Nget information in a town like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How about this place?\N--Hmm... This place seems quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, this place is lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So although this is a rough town,\Nit has a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a vacation house on the sea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, there's no one here...\Nalthough I can smell tasty food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me! Please don't\Ncome in without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This Tropical Hotel is currently\Nchartered by Bellamy-sama and his party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're asking other guests to, er... leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this place was a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If Bellamy-sama sees you, it'll be a problem,\Nso please kindly leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, what's wrong with just coming in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Bellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are those shabby guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarquiss-sama! Welcome back!\NWell, this is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind your excuses!\NJust get rid of them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think we're\Npaying to charter this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Now, go home, you dumb brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, can I beat him up?\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You're going to beat me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What funny guys! At any rate,\Nthose are rags you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Take this money and buy\Nyourselves something you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarquiss, you're wasting money\Nby giving it to guys like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have thrown\Nit down the drain instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go! This is unpleasant!\N--Hey, hey, I can walk on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarquiss! Lily! Don't tease them so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They, too, worked hard in their\Nown way to travel here. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, compared to you\Nand Bellamy, they're trash, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For average guys, they're\Ndoing better than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they probably won't be able to survive\Nin the new era that is about to start, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still... I see, 30 million... for that greenhorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show this to Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm really pissed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mock Town depends on pirates\Nwho spend lots of money, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So poor pirates aren't invited, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's no way\Nof calming you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since tough guys gather here,\Nthere's lots of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you get bothered by it each time,\Nyou can't get by in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is play it safe\Nwhen dealing with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this town is really unpleasant, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably how a\Nright-minded person would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, right-minded\Npeople are rare in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the log will be stored\Nwithin four days or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should leave before you get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four days... Then we can't stay even two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, old guy!\N--Hey, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This cherry pie tastes extremely bad! Hm?\N--This cherry pie tastes extremely good! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This drink tastes exceptionally good! Hm?\N--This drink tastes exceptionally bad! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong with your tastebuds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong with your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I'm not the cook,\NI don't care what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old guy! Give me 50 steaks to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buddy, give me 51 cherry pies to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, make that 52 steaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I want 53 pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, 54 steaks!\N--55 pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--60 steaks!\N--70 pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--80!\N--100!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you fighting about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you promised, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we don't have enough\Nmoney to buy dozens of steaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't come for shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the bounty for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million? For you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be true! It's gotta be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying! That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fighting in the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this and leave now! 50 cherry pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a pirate with a straw hat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're the 30 million bounty,\NStraw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's got business with you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Bellamy the guy chartering that hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?\NThat shorty's worth 30 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He is?\N--Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I keep running into tall guys today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your most expensive alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And give this shorty what he wants as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This place is full!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place? It's stinky and dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And cheap-looking rum\Nis about all they've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. They're from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should offer us your seats, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What hopeless dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's him, Big Knife Sarquiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to start a fight here or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:49.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deer"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole gang is here. There's\Nno way they just came for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them be! It has nothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy sure is a curious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks! You're actually a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy's nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this, small fry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't gotten any\Ninformation in this town yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm just taking him up on his offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? So you got back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're ready to take me on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! They're gonna take Bellamy on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a fight, it's a test!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Let's see how strong you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister! We want to go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did that chick... just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, if you know how\Nto get to the sky island...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "sky island"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Log Pose is\Ndefinitely pointing to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Log Pose is definitely pointing to the sky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Log Poses get broken easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys believe in such an ancient\Nlegend that there's an island in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just which era are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unusual currents in the Grand Line\Nare being explained one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Knock-Up Stream is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you probably don't know\Nsomething like that even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships that fell victim to this\Ncurrent are pushed up high in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then slam into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing this, sailors from long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saw the strange scene where the\Nships fell, and imagined sky islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking, "There must be\Nanother world in the sky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish! All phenomena have reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things that people dream\Nabout will all be explained soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief! I thought I'd test you and\Nlet you join my crew for the new era,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're such a delusional dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. The era where pirates\Ndream about things is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The City of Gold, the City of Emeralds,\Nthe big hidden treasure, One Piece...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots who are blinded by dream treasure\Ndon't notice the treasure around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this era of oceans, those who should\Nbe most capable of crossing the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are misled by those illusions and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And people talk about\Nthose dead idiots, saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He was happy since he lived his dream!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just drivel from losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see idiots chasing after\Ndreams like that, I get disgusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there're weak pirates like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it even makes us strong pirates look worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here, you scum!\NWe can't enjoy our drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy! Looks like everyone\Nhere wants to see your show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Forget the promise,\Nbeat them up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take them on, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Zoro! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. Once men decide on something,\Nyou can't make them budge an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how cool they act,\Nit's all over if they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys come and help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, we also ran into a crazy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Distinguished Pirates! A Man Who Talks of\NDreams and the King of Undersea Search!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
